        { q: 'What did her dad do that helped?', focus: 'empathy', expectedAnswer: 'He did not pick one feeling for her. He let both be real.' },
        { q: 'Is winning the only thing that makes a game good?', focus: 'perspective', expectedAnswer: 'No. Effort, growth, team, learning are all also part of it.' },
        { q: 'Have you ever had a day that was great and hard at the same time?', focus: 'reflection', expectedAnswer: 'Personal answers.' },
        { q: 'Why is "I do not know" sometimes the right answer to "how are you feeling?"', focus: 'reflection', expectedAnswer: 'Feelings can be complicated and take a while to name. Not knowing is honest.' }
