        { q: 'What does "unfair AND lucky" mean?', focus: 'empathy', expectedAnswer: 'It is sad that they live far apart, AND it is special that they get this time. Two true things.' },
        { q: 'Do you have someone in your life you only see sometimes?', focus: 'reflection', expectedAnswer: 'Personal answers.' },
        { q: 'How does love stay alive across long distances?', focus: 'reflection', expectedAnswer: 'Phone calls, letters, holding memories, traditions, the times you DO get together.' }
